No. 13981. Lawrence v. Taylor, Admr., et al. Decided November 10, 1914. Error to Circuit Court of Cuyahoga county. Messrs. Stearns, Chamberlain & Royon, for plaintiff in error. Mr. Walter C. Ong and Messrs. Squire, Sanders & Dempsey, for defendants in error. Nichols, C. J., Johnson, Wanamaker, Newman and Wilkin, JJ., concur.

Judgment affirmed.
